      "rendered": "[Webinar] Social Media for Nonprofits"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><strong>Date: Wednesday, November 6, 2024</strong><br />\n<strong>Time: 1 pm ET / 10 am PT (2 hours)<br />\nCost: $40 (USD)</strong><br />\n<strong>Presented by:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/heather-mansfield/\">Heather Mansfield</a>, Founder of Nonprofit Tech for Good</strong></p>\n<hr />\n<p>Social media is in a constant state of change and without regular education about emerging trends, your nonprofit could be wasting valuable time and resources implementing outdated best practices.</p>\n<p>From embracing Facebook &amp; Instagram Fundraising Tools to budgeting for social media ads, <a href=\"https://register.gotowebinar.com/register/6817378250474594655\">this two-hour webinar</a> will focus on what\u2019s new and next in social media so that your nonprofit can embrace being an early adopter. Topics include:</p>\n<p>\u2022\u00a0 Current best practices for using Facebook Pages and Instagram<br />\n\u2022\u00a0 What&#8217;s new in Facebook and Instagram Fundraising Tools<br />\n\u2022\u00a0 How to effectively use LinkedIn Pages and Profiles<br />\n\u2022\u00a0 An introduction to Threads for nonprofits<br />\n\u2022\u00a0 Why nonprofits need a budget for social advertising</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a0<a class=\"maxbutton-1 maxbutton maxbutton-register-now\" title=\"Register Now!\" href=\"https://register.gotowebinar.com/register/6817378250474594655\"><span class='mb-text'>Register Now!</span></a></h2>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Please Note: This webinar will be recorded. </strong>All registrants will be sent a link to the recording within 24 hours after the webinar is over. <em>There are no refunds. </em>Visit <a href=\"https://support.goto.com/webinar/system-check-attendee\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>GoToWebinar&#8217;s Attendee System Check</strong></a>\u00a0for information on how to join and attend this webinar.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>This is the final webinar in a series of three required to earn a <a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/earn-a-certificate-in-digital-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/\">Certificate in Digital Marketing &amp; Fundraising</a> from Nonprofit Tech for Good.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/earn-a-certificate-in-digital-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-37647 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Digital-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=960%2C755&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"755\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Digital-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Digital-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=300%2C236&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Digital-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=768%2C604&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Digital-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=50%2C39&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n",
